chara.name: Iroha Tamaki
chara.description: Iroha came to Kamihama to investigate strange dreams she was having. Kind-hearted, she tends to worry too much about others. She's not up on the latest trends and isn't good with her phone. Usually reserved, she can be a fighter when it matters most.

charaMessageList.message: Is this what people call...bonds?

How long...since we've eaten out
as a family?

I lied to myself...
I didn't want them to dislike me.
Welcome back. I've been waiting for you.

I'm only interfering because you're so
precious to me!
I'm sorry... Your big sis is actually...

A little bitterâ€¦ This taste brings back
such good memories.
Good thing I didn't give up!
I had faith that we'd be okay.
Your big sis did it!
Have I become a strong big sis?

This Doppel wordlessly wraps around and strangles anything it doesn't want to hear as it continues its search for something to fill the hole in its heart. While it should be calling for someone, it is cowardly and afraid of acknowledging the reality it has concealed, and so it remains, silently covering its ears.

chara.name: Yachiyo Nanami
chara.description: A seasoned Magical Girl who has fought Witches for 7 years in Kamihama. Yachiyo is well informed about the city and Magical Girls in general. She keeps her distance from other Magical Girls while she compiles files on the Rumors of Kamihama City.

charaMessageList.message:
I hope you learned your lesson
and won't do it again.
I don't see my donut. Where is it?
All right. I accept your challenge.
We Magical Girls must not harm each other.
Listen. We are on the same side...
Life as a Magical Girl isn't easy.

I will protect everyone
no matter what happens.
I survived again...
Well, that ended okay.
I will not die! Not here!
I will protect you... I promise.

The light from the lantern at the end of the Doppel's tail can call forth a myriad of illusions, and the scissors are said to cause great devastation in the near futures of those who have been harmed by them. As Magical Girls get older, their emotional range becomes smaller, and such is the case for this master, who cannot separate her body from her Doppel.

chara.name: Tsuruno Yui
chara.description: A reckless Magical Girl who's full of energy. Tsuruno loves her family, especially her grandfather and great-grandfather, who lead the Yuis to their former prosperity. She fights to become the strongest Magical Girl in order to restore the Yui name.

charaMessageList.message:
But I wanted to train harde
and become even mightier!
We all start out with equal strength!

If you're strong enough,
ANYTHING is possible!

Impulsive? Reckless?
What does that even mean?!
Ugh... I got yelled atâ€¦ Again!
Yay! I'm the Mightiest Magical Girl!
Yeah! YEAH! This is what I call training!
I feel like I'm getting even more powerful!
I'm telling ya! I can't lose!
This proves how mighty I REALLY am!
Ya gotta admit it! Right now I am the mightiest!

doppel.title: Feature: Ham
doppel.description: The master of this emotion is unhappy with both the appearance and behavior of her Doppel. In contrast to her own desires to achieve great deeds through her own hard work, this Doppel creates a stream of wealth to satisfy the desires of her relatives in an attempt to preserve family peace. Though this is only a short-lived harmony. She believes that it exists in contrast to her own goals and prefers to keep it hidden. However, she may one day find that she needs this Doppel to protect the harmony between her family, no matter how fragile that harmony might be.

chara.name: Sana Futaba
chara.description: A pessimistic Magical Girl, Sana was rejected by her family and those around her, so she has hardly any self-confidence. However, she'll quietly stand by the people who need her, ready to help them when the time comes.

charaMessageList.message: Am I far away? Or is it something else?
Cats' eyes are so clear and pretty!
Oh, please don't mind me...
The scenery around me seems kind of hazy.
It's not that I like being alone...
Why was I even born?
I wonder what Iroha's doing now...
I'm so glad... We're alive...
Huh? Really? We won?
Whew... I think we got lucky.
Um... Am I...strong?

The main body of this Doppel is not the chair, but an invisible entity that is tortured endlessly while sitting atop it. This transparent Doppel uses its own blood to attack its enemies; however, it is not so easily controlled, and should the visible Doppel emerge from its master's right ear instead of the invisible one that typically appears from her left ear, it will scream and go on a rampage, swinging its guillotine at allies and enemies alike.

chara.name: Felicia Mitsuki
chara.description: Felicia is a spirited Magical Girl, full of energy and determination, who hates Witches for taking the lives of her parents. She now works as a mercenary, hunting Witches all across Kamihama. Her tough talk hides a kind heart and a love of animals.

charaMessageList.message: Hey, you! Wanna hire me?
UGH! Annoying stuff is so lame!
Don't sweat it! I don't ask for much.
My style? I go BAM, enemies go SPLAT!
Leave 'em to me! I'm super duper strong!
Don't hurt yourself! Need some help?
I'll wipe 'em out all by myself!
Yay! I won!
Ha! That's no way to fight!
Yep. Turned out exactly as you'd expect.
Lose? What does that even mean?

doppel.description: The master of this emotion falls into a deep sleep while this Doppel is present, and is therefore unable to witness what it experiences. While its master is sleeping, it paints over all inconveniences with muddy tears that flow from its vacant stare. This duplicate will surely awaken when it requires the power to crush reality.

chara.name: Mifuyu Azusa
chara.description: Seven years ago, she fought as Yachiyo's partner. After noticing that her magic was weakening, she joined the Wings of the Magius as one of their leaders, hoping to secure happiness for herself. Though kind and gentle, her spirit is weak, which leads her to make bad decisions from time to time.

charaMessageList.message: I will bear the weight of my sins.
All I wanted was to be an ordinary girl...
I willl save both mine and Yachan's souls.
Mm, I'd love a steamed bun right now!
I remember every one of Yachan's letters.

Would you like to sit in a cafe and
read with me?
A sugary sweet drama can still be charming!
I'm so relieved everyone is okay.
I could've pushed myself harder back in the day.
I hope I'm not deceiving myself with this victory.
I can keep holding my head high for now.

doppel.title: Feature: Aviary
doppel.description: The master of this emotion will use all powers at her disposal to stay alive in this reality, including this all-in-one Doppel. Countless bird-shaped minions known as "Sugar Geese" emerge from her shadows on the ground, attacking her foes on command. The mere touch of a Sugar Goose will cause its target to taste such sweetness that it will inspire a maddening addiction. This makes it easy to make targets accept most lies, even with just a few geese. The Doppel sprouts from the tongue and arms, so she cannot speak while using it.

cardSkill.name: You Just Can't Live Without Me

chara.name: Touka Satomi
chara.description: A Magical Girl who is working to create a world without Witches. The daughter, and patient, of the director of the Satomi Medical Center, Touka is an astrophysics prodigy. Surrounded by a wall of gadgets and devices, she continues to research her one dream...to know everything about the universe.

charaMessageList.message: Maybe transmitting radio waves is better?
Too bad!
The universe is my only freedom.
Nemu's being stubborn again.
Did you know stars have a language too?

*Giggle* To think I can freely use
the radio telescope!

I wonder what my uncle saw
before he vanished...
I'm so amazing! Hee hee!
Yes, yes! I feel so charged up!
I think we worked hard. Good job.
I won't let anyone stand in the way of human evolution!

doppel.description: The master of this emotion desires more power even after becoming a Magical Girl, in order to achieve more wishes. This Doppel divides its master's lifespan up into matches, and grants a "What If" wish whenever a match is lit. When the Doppel runs out of matches, the master's life is over. It is very powerful, but similar to the Doppel of Dying Wishes, it mustn't be abused, for it sacrifices one's own lifespan.

chara.name: Alina Gray
chara.description: A Magical Girl who is trying to create a world where no one has to become a Witch, Alina is an artistic genius obsessed with life and death who pours herself into her work, dreaming of making masterpieces featuring Witches themselves. She's used herself as a subject for her art when in a creative slump.

charaMessageList.message: All I want to see is the best art ever made!

That girl's beloved manga,
it's just as ridicolo as she is.
No...this isn't right... No, not at all!
I myself will be my final masterpiece!
Che palle! Still aliveâ€¦

I, Alina,
will NEVER concede to artist's block!

If you're going to lie to yourself,
you might as well be dead.
Oh, I just got so excited...
*Sigh* I, Alina, have grown tired of this...
I could never get tired of this.
You are not worthy to be used in my artwork.

doppel.description: The master of this Doppel is entranced by the beauty of her own Doppel, but has yet to realize that it is still hiding its true form. It attacks from where it sprouts out of her back, using a large projection of itself made from the hardened paint (Pathogen Tempera) it emits. It boasts a Witch-like figure as it does this, despite its Doppel nature â€” this is because its human body becomes so coated in paint that she's no longer visible. The master cannot verify the appearance of her Doppel, but apparently it is "just as beautiful when you view it from the inside".

chara.name: Rena Minami
chara.description: A Magical Girl who has trouble opening up to others. Rena acts cocky to make up for her lack of self-confidence, which leads people who don't know her well to misunderstanding her. She's a picky eater and loves sweets. She is also a big fan of idols.

charaMessageList.message: Oh, Momoko... What're you doing now?!
O-okay then... Become my servant!
I'm back to being alone...
Hehe...I love this concert DVD!
You're the one who started this fight!!
Even I hate me...
I told you! I'm not mad at you at all!!
This result seems quite natural to me, y'know?
You're not bad.
This is all thanks to you. Thank you.
It's definitely high five time!

doppel.description: The master of this emotion uses its power to their utmost content. This Doppel enhances the transforming ability of its possessor manyfold, allowing her to transform into someone else for a certain amount of time. The result of this transformation is truer to the ideal image of the person than the actual person it is based on. However, because the transformation is so perfect, if it is used too much, the user is likely to lose track of their own identity. It turns the user into the ideal state of its target, so it sometimes appears slightly different from the original.

chara.name: Momoko Togame
chara.description: A Magical Girl who is always looking out for rookies. The middle child, Momoko was influenced by her two brothers' boyishness, but she loves cute, girly things like stuffed animals. Because she loves cute things she's also a fan of female idols.

charaMessageList.message: Is it wrong? I love idols!
Why'd I become a Magical Girl againâ€¦?

Call me a meddler if you want.
I can't just ignore this!
Me likin' somethin' like thisâ€¦it's weird, huh?
Why've I grown into such a tough girl?
My team's well-balanced! Don't you think?
Aww...I always have the worst timing!
Neat and clean, just the way I like it!
It's all about team work, right?
I'm countin' on you to back me up from here on!
All of us are here! It was bound to turn out like this.

doppel.title: Feature: Nails
doppel.description: The master of this emotion cares not where its power fly. This Doppel attacks with its huge fingers, along with the many fingers that fly around it. All the nails on the fingers are polished and decorated. It cares very much about its nails. When someone praises them, it becomes quite happy, but when someone says something bad about them, it gets discouraged and depressed. It is quite troublesome to deal with when this happens, so it is a good idea to let it attack the enemy as soon as you summon it.

cardSkill.name: So What If I'm Overbearing?!

chara.name: Kaede Akino
chara.description: A worrywart, Kaede is easily scared. She is also kind, caring, and ready to take risks for her friends. She loves animals, plants, and insects, and nature in general. She enjoys gardening, and though she's not good at them, she likes UFO Catchers.

charaMessageList.message: Why did I agree to become a Magical Girl?
This way! W-wait! No, this way!
That's so m-mean! Um...I...I'm sorry...
I want to be your teammate again...!
I keep holding them back...
Oh, no! I spent 5,000 yen on this...
Huh? Oh, wh-what should I do?!
I won...right?
What a reliefâ€¦
Wow! Amazing!
Iâ€¦I can do it too!

doppel.title: Feature: Plot of Land
doppel.description: The master of this emotion fears that it will eat away at their everyday life and carefully chooses when to summon it, for the instant this Doppel is summoned, regardless of its master's intentions, it will cover its surroundings with rotten moss to conquer the land, with its only goal being to expand its territory. Summoning this Doppel accidentally, even in a beloved area, will destroy its surroundings by covering everything in its moss. Within the confines of its territory, it can unleash tremendous power.

chara.name: Karin Misono
chara.description: The "Magical Girl born of Halloween". Or that's what she says at least... Karin loves reading and drawing manga so much that she's even created her own Magical Girl persona. She's heavily influenced by her favorite manga, Phantom Thief Magical Kirin.

charaMessageList.message:
I have so many fond memories of
Magical Kirin!

I want Alina-senpai to give me
some drawing lessons!

I'm Magical Karin,
savior of weak Magical Girls!

Halloween is special.
It's the day I came into being!

Thanks to everyone,
I found a new way to live my life!
I WILL save my grandmother!
Trick or... No, wait! Trick AND treat!
Now THIS is a Happy Halloween!
There's nothing this scythe can't cut down!
If you bring me candy next time, I'll let ya slide!
This is the power of a demon from the underworld!

It shares its proclivity for thievery with its master, and will pilfer anything it can get its hands on, even if those items belong to an ally. This Doppel is extremely greedy and refuses to give up anything once it has it in its possession.

chara.name: Asuka Tatsuki
chara.description: An assistant Naginata instructor at the Ryushinkan Dojo and Magical Girl. As the only child of the Dojo Master, she trains hard every day. She is disciplined, but also absentminded, and that absentmindedness can get her into trouble.

charaMessageList.message:
Oof!
This is Asuka Tatsuki's worst blunder ever!

I-I'm going to kill myself!
Don't try to stop me!
I regret nothing!
I have no choice but to use my last resort!
I will not run...or hide...or disappear!
Stop toying with me!

If I give up now,
it'd be a disgrace to Ryushin-ryu!
Victory is mine!
This is the way of Ryushin-ryu!
Never let your guard down, even after victory!
We won! Let me hear a triumphant cheer!

doppel.name: Doppel of Assault
doppel.title: Feature: War Drum
doppel.description: The master of this emotion is eager to become stronger through her Doppel's power. It energizes itself with the beat of its drum and sends out orders to turn its allies into valiant warriors. However, it also shares its master's hastiness, so once the order is given, its allies are forced to perform an act of utter disgrace against their will. Its reputation with its allies is terrible as a result of this unreasonableness. It is difficult to handle as, like its master, it attempts to kill itself after committing a blunder.

chara.name: Nemu Hiiragi
chara.description: A Magical Girl who is working to create a world without Witches. Nemu started writing stories just trying to seek some approval, it wasn't until she posted those same stories online that she become known as a literary genius. Her dream is to wrap the world in her stories...literally.

charaMessageList.message:
The fate of Magical Girls,
and the choices we make.

All of the interwoven stories are
finally taking a unified shape!

It was beyond a miracle that
I was discharged from the hospital.

My brother and I aren't close.
He's almost a stranger to me.
Touka's acting wild again...
Magical Girls are isolated and lonely...

Let's leave our mark,
so that people know we were here.
The story ends here.
You gave up on your story here, not me.
My story knows no end.
My creations are for everyone.

cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [V] / Guaranteed Charm, Curse, and Blind (Target/1 Turn) / ATK UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages a Single Enemy [IX] / Guaranteed Charm, Curse, and Blind (Target/1 Turn) / Remove Buffs (Target) / ATK UP (Team/3 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Dying Wishes
doppel.title: Feature: Wood Beetle
doppel.description: The master of this emotion will sacrifice everything she has. This terrifying Doppel uses both of its bug-headed hands to devour the stories of the world. It can then use its ridiculous power to materialize these stories into the real world. It is said its power comes from its weakening master, and that as she gets weaker, the Doppel get stronger. However since it uses all of its power to materialize the stories it eats it doesn't pack a physical punch, some even believe it wouldn't stand a chance against a direct hit from a Witch.

chara.name: Ui Tamaki
chara.description: A Magical Girl who is struggling to figure out what she can do to make everyone happy. She grew up knowing little of the outside, which is why she tries so hard to keep up with others. Skilled at finding the good in people, she dislikes no one. Touka and Nemu are her close friends, and Iroha is her sister.

charaMessageList.message: The outside world is amazing...
Stop, no more fighting!
My dream is to sing in the school chorus.

Living like this...
It's all I need to be happy.

I have to hurry and become
more independent!
I wonder what kind of adult I'll become?

Wow, I made my first friend
on the outside!
Hey Sis, I was able to beat them!
Yeah, my power's getting steadier now!
Thanks, little sparrow!
I can help now, I think.

doppel.title: Feature: The Happy Statue
doppel.description: The master of this emotion shares in all the pain of the ones she loves and takes it on as her own. The pain then takes the shape of jewels, which decorate the Doppel and add to its power. However, as the Doppel cannot move, it cannot avoid attacks, and though it carries a sword and shield, they are there for decorative purposes only.

cardSkill.name: Is it Okay for a Newbie Like Me?!
cardSkill.shortDescription: ATK UP [IX] / Ignore Reduce Damage / Guaranteed Curse

chara.name: Kanagi Izumi
chara.description: A Magical Girl whose goal is peace and equality. Altruistic and of strong moral character, her powerful words and demeanor lend her a certain kind of charisma that draws people to her. She devotes herself to her multiple part-time jobs to help support her struggling family.

charaMessageList.message:
Serving customers is more
challenging than I thought.

Hurry up and choose
something to eat, Master.

I must study more anime,
manga, and games.

Our finances are in tatters.
They could collapse at any moment.

THIS is why we've been persecuted
for so long...?

It's a huge pain when evil
disguises itself as justice.

We must set this town ablaze,
for it is rotten to the core.
I suppose that could've been worse.
My boss is calling, I need to hurry to work!
Life and death are granted to us in equal measure.
Curse your own actions, then atone for them.

cardMagia.shortDescription: Deals 5 Random Hits [V] / Negate Evade Chance (Team/1 Turn) / Reduce Damage Chance (Self/1 Turn)

doppel.name: Doppel of Demolition
doppel.title: Feature: Hearth Lion
doppel.description: The master of this emotion is coolheaded, but her Doppel is burning with endless rage. Its form is a rampaging lion that rends all around it to pieces with its gnashing teeth. It refuses to forgive the smallest of injustices and demolishes anything it deems irrational. Strictness incarnate, it may target others simply for living in Kamihama, so its master must take care when summoning it, lest it hurt her allies. If she continues to use this Doppel, she may become similarly unforgiving. It may be uncontrollable, but its master half agrees with its judgment.

chara.name: Mitama Yakumo
chara.description: A Magical Girl who operates as a Coordinator in the outskirts of Kamihama. Unable to fight for herself, she accepts Grief Seeds in exchange for items and providing magical adjustments. Though she usually has a sunny disposition and a friendly smile, very few Magical Girls know her true nature.

charaMessageList.message:
Hello!
What can the Coordinator do for you?

Are you here for an adjustment
Some items? A chat?
I'm sorry. Really, I'm only teasing you.

Just a warning,
you shouldn't take me lightly, or else!
Surely I'm destined to live a life of regret.
Yes, I love everyone, and hate everyone.

Wiping everything away
would feel so nice.
My my, not too shabby, if I do say so myself!
I'm so nervous, my heart is pounding...
Your Coordinator would appreciate a compliment or two!
Thank you, everyone, you're all a big help.

doppel.title: Feature: Flower Petals
doppel.description: The master of this Doppel resents her environment and wishes to destroy everything. Her Doppel never forgets that death comes to all things equally. It covers everything with dancing flower petals and escorts girls elegantly with its white gloves. Like its master, it isn't able to attack directly, but its power, which is connected to the end of all things, is utterly terrifying - the magic of anything hidden under its flower petals rots away to nothing. The more the master relies on this Doppel, the closer her left arm will get to becoming completely one with it.

cardSkill.name: I Hope You Can Afford Thisâ™ª
cardSkill.shortDescription: Heal [IX] / Damage UP on Enemies with Status Ailments [IX] / DEF DOWN [V]

chara.name: Tsukuyo Amane
chara.description: Tsukasa's twin sister, Tsukuyo hopes to liberate Magical Girls. Constant training in music, calligraphy, and dance has granted her considerable skills. Though she is admired by her peers, she doesn't have any friends she feels she can open up to. She can only be at peace when she is with her sister, Tsukasa.

charaMessageList.message: Are you my sister?
My father's flute held a secret.
Tsuruno Yui...and Felicia Mitsuki?!
She was strikingly similar to myself.
I never want to despise Tsukasa...
We're spitting images of one another!
Oh Mother, just who am I?!
We have triumphed!
Perseverance bears fruit once again.
Thank you for your attention.
Thus concludes our performance.

cardSkill.shortDescription: Damage After Using Charge UP [IX] / Critical Hit Chance [VII] / Connecting with Tsukasa will boost her ATK

cardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Stronger Elemental Damage to All Enemies [VII] / Damage After Using Charge UP (Team/5 Turns)

doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Stronger Elemental Damage to All Enemies [IX] / Damage After Using Charge UP (Team/5 Turns)

doppel.name: Doppel of Seclusion
doppel.title: Feature: Terrarium
doppel.description: The master of this Doppel isn't swayed by mood or emotion. She does, however, rely on her other half, the only person who truly understands her. Through this, the two of them are capable of completely isolating themselves from the outside. Together in their miniature world, they need only the company of the other to survive. This Doppel shuts out all physical and magical phenomena, allowing its master to perfectly protect herself and her twin. Though doing so causes their memories of anyone but each other to fade away.

cardSkill.name: Our Sound Resonates as One
cardSkill.shortDescription: Damage After Using Charge UP [XI] / Critical Hit Chance [IX] / Connecting with Tsukasa will boost her ATK

chara.name: Tsukasa Amane
chara.description: Tsukuyo's twin sister, Tsukasa hopes to liberate Magical Girls. Born into a family of traditional bamboo craftsmen, she runs the household to support her father and his apprentices. Though she is cheerful and has many friends, Tsukuyo is the only one she can open up to.

charaMessageList.message: You, you're my sister?
Dad, how could you hide this from me?
Who is that? She looks just like me.

Being happy and energetic
makes other people happy!
I never want to hate Tsukuyo...
Sorry, everyone! I'm going shopping now!
Um, am I really an only child?
Great job, everyone!
It's all thanks to the smiles!
Our performance is over. Thank you very much!
You don't need an encore, right?

doppel.title: Feature: Aquarium
doppel.description: The master of this emotion will not bend or break to any situation or circumstance, but she will lose herself utterly in her other half, the only person who truly understands her. Through this, the two are capable of severing their connection to the world outside. No matter the opinion or attitude taken, together in their miniature world they can only trust each other's presence. No one else can understand them. This Doppel shuts out any unknown values in order to keep its master's spirit stable, though doing so causes her sense of ethics to weaken.

cardSkill.name: This is Our Harmony
cardSkill.shortDescription: Charges MP [VIII] / Connecting with Tsukuyo will restore extra MP

chara.name: Iroha Tamaki
chara.title: Swimsuit
chara.description: A Magical Girl enjoying summer vacation with her friends. Her swimsuit is a Magical Girl outfit, so she can fight at any time, but she's equipped with a swim float in case of water battles as she's not a confident swimmer... She can also use it to escape in an emergency by twisting it like a screw.

charaMessageList.message: This swim float and I are inseparable!
Nooo, I can't! I can't let go of my float!

I'll try to swim at least 5 meters...
Nothing too crazy!

When I start swimming,
my whole mind goes blank in panic...

Hee hee...
Fish are really amazing, hee hee...

Ah, Tsuruno!
Keep hold of my hand!

There's no stopping me
if I have a kickboard!
I think...I managed to swim the whole way?
I wonder if there's some way I'll be able to swim...
I just have to keep pushing forward!
This feeling... Maybe I can swim now?!

doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Deals Damage in a Vertical Line [IX] / DEF DOWN (Vertical/3 Turns) / Accele MP UP (Team/3 Turns) / Heal (Team)

doppel.name: Doppel of Silence
doppel.title: Feature: Cuckoo
doppel.description: The master of this emotion is in the slow process of accepting herself on her journey to find her sister. Her excitement for the summer has also made her a bit cheerier. This mood is reflected in the Doppel's clothing and mast, giving the impression that it's being unreasonably influenced by its master's temporary emotional state. In other words, its appearance is only skin-deep. Despite being optimized for battle at sea, its master cannot swim, which hinders its movements somewhat. It simply attacks enemies in front of it with all the power at its disposal.

cardSkill.name: I Can't Swim, Is That Okay?!
cardSkill.shortDescription: Blast Damage UP [X] / DEF UP [X] / Guaranteed Fog

chara.name: Uwasa Tsuruno
chara.description: A Magical Girl who serves as the mascot (Uwasa) of Chelation Land. She spends her time completely relaxed, protecting the theme park that rids its visitors of all worries. Her suggestions for the food court menu impressed all the other Uwasa.

charaMessageList.message: Welcome to Chelation Land!
No need to go back to Mikazuki Villa.

I'm sure Dad's upset but...
it's gotta be this way.

Hmm... What food and merch
should we stock...

Don't you wish you had
a mane like mine?

You don't have to try
to be happy here!
All right! It's time to fuse!
Everyone can exit the venue now!
All you need to do is go with the flow!
Hey, now it's time to chill out!
I can feel safe here.

doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [IX] / ATK DOWN / MP Gain DOWN (All Foes/2 Turns) / Guaranteed Evade (Self/1 Turn)

doppel.name: Doppel of Camaraderie
doppel.title: Feature: Ham
doppel.description: Have you heard? Has anybody told you? The Rumor of the Doppel of Camaraderie! It's a little pig that's grown nice and plump, capable of granting wishes for its master's family. It represents great wealth with its grand, glittering body, and ensures her family's wealth in the years to come! However, the master of this piggy doesn't much care for it, it actually puts her in quite the grumpy mood. "It's way too embarrassing to let anyone see it!" she says, so she hides it. It's a hot rumor in Kamihama!  No, stop, don't look!

chara.name: Holy Alina
chara.description: A Magical Girl dressed in her own art, themed upon the base nature of mankind. In order to gather the energy necessary for this form, she warms those with frozen hearts in exchange for years off their life. She also creates a death mask of her target, but that's an unrelated artistic pursuit of hers.

charaMessageList.message: Let me warm your cold soul.
Ah haha! I, Alina, have found my beauty!

My final work will surely
come to fruition in an instant.
Behold my beautiful installation.
That idiota's stupid manga is so...
As a human, I too yearn for this beauty...
Perhaps I, Alina, should just change this world.
I went ahead and took a couple years off your life in exchange.
Ah, I can see it... It's just so thrilling...
For the sake of my art, I will one day engulf this world.
I want you to imagine a world in ruin.

doppelCardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [â…©] / Status Ailment Resistance DOWN (All Foes/3T) / Guaranteed Bewitch (All Foes/1T) / DEF DOWN (Self/1T)

doppel.name: Doppel of Fever
doppel.title: Feature: Piping Bag
doppel.description: The master of this emotion believes that the art it seeks and the art humanity desires subconsciously are one and the same, and she gathers energy to make that art reality. The joy of the realization that the universal theme of humanity is the manifestation of an individual's emotion is reflected in this Doppel's appearance. Not only does it experience euphoria, but its pathogenetic tempera paint also shines with brilliant hues. However, the pain it inflicts and the suffering it endures are one and the same. Its victims' death rattles like echoes accolades in its master's ears.

cardSkill.name: The Art Humanity Desires
cardSkill.shortDescription: ATK UP [IX] / Guaranteed Curse / Stun Chance

chara.name: Mitama Yakumo
chara.title: Kimono
chara.description: A Magical Girl who works hard and plays hard from the first day of the year. She is very fond of the kimono that she got from Yachiyo, so she infused it with magic, and she's now able to wear it during battle. With her cards as her weapon, she directs her attacks at those who fail to play her game correctly.

charaMessageList.message: Perfect weather to visit a shrine.

I've already decided on
my New Year's resolution.

I was so excited wearing a kimono
for the first time in the new year.

Come to your Coordinator
with your troublesâ™ª

Butter and chocolate are a must
for sweet porridgeâ™ª

My first dream of the year was
a little strange this time.

I'm still young enough to receive money
on New Year's.
I'll buy some tangerines on my way home.
Yayâ™ª This is the card I needed!
Let's see what your fortune is... Oh no, "Terrible Luck".
What an auspicious way to start the new yearâ™ª

cardMagia.shortDescription: Damages All Enemies [V] / Guaranteed Curse / Magia Seal Chance (All Foes/1 Turn)

doppel.title: Feature: Auspicious Day
doppel.description: The master of this emotion is happy to welcome the new year with newly made friends, despite resenting her situation. That happiness takes the form of golden lilies, as well as red and white striped cloth. She shares her joy by scattering flowers about everyone nearby before wrapping them in the cloth to ring in the new year. Then again, no one is allowed to go home when it's time to serve the New Year's feast, so they languish in agony as they endure an eternal end to the year.

cardSkill.name: To Another Wonderful Year!
cardSkill.shortDescription: Heal [VIII] / ATK UP [VII] / Damage UP on Enemies with Status Ailments [V]

chara.name: Amane Sisters
chara.title: Swimsuit
chara.description: Twin Magical Girls who sing the praises of summer. With one steering the banana boat and the other wielding a water gun, these two prove to be quite the combo. Since they're skipping out on their duties of the workshop and the Magius, they'd prefer to keep their ocean escapades a secret.

charaMessageList.message:
Huh, Iroha Tamaki?!
What are YOU doing here?!
Wh-what exactly is a banana boat?

Is it really okay for me
to stay like this?

The bobbing of the waves is
so soothing.

The ocean is gorgeous! I'm so glad
I came with Tsukuyo...

I'm so happy to see Tsukasa
having so much fun.

I've never had so much fun
during the summer before!
*Sigh* Finally, we can go back into the water...
This banana boat is very heavy...
"We caught such a huge wave that time!" "For sure!"
"Victory is ours!" "For sure!"

doppel.title: Feature: Terrarium
doppel.description: The masters of this emotion have forgotten the darkness inside one another and become completely absorbed in playing at their own private resort. This Doppel typically makes magic out of moonlight, but it has been overcome with affection for the sun, and now creates it from sunlight. As a result it bounces around gleefully, causing tragedy to all those around it, erasing that which it touches from existence and leaving pandemonium in its wake. Since it has none of the five senses, even should one scream in agony, those screams do not reach it.

cardSkill.name: Summertime Resonance
cardSkill.shortDescription: Charges MP [VIII] / Critical Hit Chance [IX] / Remove Status Ailments

chara.name: Iroha & Yachiyo
chara.title: Final Battle
chara.description: This Magical Girl pair was able to obtain a strength that supported them during a battle with an overwhelmingly strong Witch. Although they started off as enemies, they wound up becoming the best of friends, connected by an unbreakable bond. Their wings can only be seen the moment that power is ready.

charaMessageList.message: M-me?! But I've never modeled before!

This is back from when I used to work
in a modeling group.

If it's okay for us to just be
ourselves, then...

I can see how people would
think we're sisters.
We'll always be together...forever! Winkâ˜†

It's been a while since I've felt
so excited for work.

This month is going to be tough
for Mikazuki Villa...
You really thought you could catch us off guard?
Our bond led us to victory, right?
"Are you okay, Yachiyo?" "Yes, I'm fine thanks to you."
"The feathers helped us win." "There's no more need for despair."

chara.description: A Magical Girl with extraordinary potential who lives in Mitakihara with her parents and younger brother. Gentle and caring, she is always surrounded by friends. She uses a bow and arrow in battle.

charaMessageList.message: Hmmm... Which ribbon should I wear?

I don't know much about this city...
It sure is strange, though...
I'm a Magical Girlâ€¦so I have to do this!
Is thisâ€¦real?
Were you the one who was calling me?
Don't tell anyone in class, okay?
If I'm awesome, it'll all work out!
Thank goodness...it looks like we've won!
We did it! Great!
Yes! Looking good!
Phew... We made it through somehow!

doppel.description: The master of this emotion tries to save all of existence. This Doppel appears as a huge floating Soul Gem. Once it is summoned, it creates an existence within which all things around it are consumed, and then takes control of everything within that existence. After that, it floats higher into the air and a shower of light arrows rains down. While all of this is happening, the master of this emotion sleeps inside the huge Soul Gem.

chara.name: Homura Akemi
chara.description: A mysterious Magical Girl who transferred into Madoka's class. She repeatedly travels through time to save her friend from a fate of despair, preparing to defeat Walpurgisnacht without the aid of anyone else. She is from a different timeline than the Homura who found herself in Kamihama.

charaMessageList.message: This has nothing to do with you.
I swear it, I promise I'll save you!

I'll keep going back,
as many times as it takes.
I won't rely on anyone anymore.

Think about the people that care
deeply about you, too.
You see, I...I come from the future.

I don't care if I have to stay locked
in this endless maze.
I won't lose here!
A moment later and you would have been dead.
I will not stop fighting!
Are we done? I'm going up ahead.

doppel.description: The master of this emotion visits many worlds in search of an exit, spinning giant threads of fate. Fourteen incomplete bodies born from emotion trail behind the master's body, which has almost completely transformed into glass. In order to achieve their mission, these 14 bodies work methodically and tirelessly to remove obstacles. Regardless of their master's will, they weave the threads of fate, which become tangled in ever more complex patterns, driving her yet further into a maze, the exit of which can hardly be found. These bodies of emotion have no names.

chara.title: Glasses
chara.description: A timid Magical Girl who wished to protect Madoka. She turns back time repeatedly in an attempt to prevent Madoka from becoming a Witch. Now she searches for a new hope in Kamihama City.

charaMessageList.message: I... I want to redo my meeting with Madoka!
I want to be someone who can protect her...
Where am I? What is this place...
I'll never, ever give up!
Which weapon should I use this time?
Let's do our best together from now on!
I'll save Madoka for sure this time!
I did it? I did it!
Phew...it's over now...
I got through it...somehow...
Did I fight wellâ€¦?

doppel.title: Feature: The Mortal World
doppel.description: The master of this emotion loops through time in an endless cycle of trial-and-error. Master and Doppel fuse together, her skin becomes glass, and her expression freezes into that of a doll. She launches volley after volley of attacks that only end when her target falls silent. In this way she is more like a Witch than other Magical Girls. Not only can she can manipulate the sands of time, but she can pluck information of low importance from the alien lifeforms on her hat and create anything around the level of an earthly weapon by solidifying the sand.

chara.name: Sayaka Miki
chara.description: A straightforward Magical Girl with a strong sense of justice. She is a dear friend of Madoka, who also lives in Mitakihara. She looks up to her Magical Girl senpai, Mami, and her fighting style of mass-conjuring weapons resembles hers. She used to visit her childhood friend Kyosuke in the hospital often.

charaMessageList.message: Never thought I'd be doing detective work!

I can't believe we're going to hang out
together again! Am I dreaming?

I wonder if I'll be able to find some
rare CDs in Kamihama.

To think there were so many
Magical Girls out there!
Why did it have to be us?

Alright, time to kill myself some
Witches today!

Magic really exists, and miracles
really do happen.
Case closed, I guess!
Sheesh, that was cutting it close!
Is it okay to praise myself for that?
I almost dozed off from sheer boredom there!

doppel.title: Feature: Mermaid
doppel.description: The master of this emotion suffered from young love and chose a fate so harsh that she could not bear it alone. As such, the Doppel dreams of love while it swims effortlessly through the air, playing a song for its master from its vast hollow body. It can control several swords to attack its enemies with the soundwaves that emanate from its body, but as long as the master uses it, she cannot flee from the discontent that troubles her heart.

chara.name: Mami Tomoe
chara.description: A Magical Girl who has been fighting Witches in Mitakihara longer than the others. She is experienced and takes care of Madoka and her friends. She is proud of being able to save people, and loves tea.

charaMessageList.message: This town is like a maze. I feel so uncertain...

Believe in yourself and fight.
The rest will follow.
Shall we have a tea break?
Being a Magical Girl is no walk in the park.

What dream do you intend to
make a reality?
What's going on in in this cityâ€¦?
Ohâ€¦ Could you beat me on equal footing?
One job done.
Phew... That was close!
All right then. Time for some tea.
Want to come to my place after this?

This Doppel is very small compared to other Doppels and always sits on its master's head, so the master is hardly aware of it. It is doubtful that they communicate, so its master fights normally while it supports her. It is small and looks unreliable, but its vines are powerful enough to penetrate any enemy.

chara.name: Kyoko Sakura
chara.description: Kyoko is a Magical Girl from Kazamino who doesn't seem to go to school or have a home. Defiant and pragmatic, she often butts heads with other Magical Girls. She wields a multi-jointed spear, and can create magical barriers. She is always snacking.

charaMessageList.message: Ya look like ya stress out real easy.
Naive Magical Girls get killed quick.
...Well, a free meal's a free meal.
I'm gonna survive no matter what.
I can't just ignore idiots like that.
If ya get it, then don't be a dumbass.
Substance over style, that's me.
I'll take the win, thanks!
Well that went well!
Now then. What to eat?
They're gonna feel that one!

doppel.description: The master of this emotion doesn't trust its mysterious power, she only borrows its weapon and wields it herself. To the master, it's is no more than a hateful thing that drags up her painful past due to its power, a dubious hypnotic magic that controls mist to produce illusions. But even still, it possesses her regrets, hidden deep in her heart, so she allows it to aid her somewhat in battle, though she remains suspicious of it. The Doppel itself is the fluttering kimono-like thing, while the candlestick holder the master rides is a separate being altogether.

chara.name: Nagisa Momoe
chara.description: She once brought hope...and then a curse. Guided by the Law of Cycles, she has come to Kamihama as a messenger. Her thoughts quickly turn to cheese, her one and only obsession, even when she is on a mission.

charaMessageList.message: *Sniff, sniff* I know this smell... It's cheese!
Let me explain.
I just wanted to have cheese one more time.
Mmm... Cheddaaar!!!
So that's Mami Tomoe...
I'm going to eat that, and that, and that...
Oh, I'm so full... I'm taking a break...
We won! *Sigh* Good grief...
Now I can take my time eating this cheese!
Great! It's snack time!
Thanks for the food! I ate ALL of it!

She may behave in a shameful manner at times, but in her heart is a well of deep love. The Doppel does not fuse with its host; rather, it emerges as a mask from her nose, which then covers her face completely. The host does not move while her Doppel is present. chara.title: Kimono
chara.description: A Magical Girl who goes to school in Mitakihara City. The power from her wish has infused her kimono, and now she can battle while wearing it. Her weapon is now a hanetsuki paddle, good for both close and long range attacks. Look closely at her paddle and you may see someone you recognize...

charaMessageList.message:
What was everyone's first dream
of the year like?

See this ribbon?
I got it tied especially for today!

Yep, hanetsuki is the best thing
to play on New Year's!

Hmm... What should I write for
my New Year's resolution?

Isn't visiting the shrine on New Year's
morning exciting?!

Remember, happiness is
what brings fortune!

Look at everyone's kimonos!
They're so lovely!
There's some New Year's treats waiting for me at home!
I have to get home so I can eat some mochi!
Looks like we'll be having a great year!
We all have to get together and celebrate!

Any and all life that has thrived on this earth over the millenia of its existence are sure to be equally condensed and crushed by the enormity of this fleeting creature's wish.

cardSkill.name: Let's Make This a Great Year!

chara.name: Ultimate Madoka
chara.description: A Goddess who watches over Magical Girls from the furthest reaches of the universe's present, past, and future. She knows all there is to know about Magical Girls and provides blessings for all of them, but for the first time since coming into being, she found a Magical Girl she does not recognize...

charaMessageList.message: I really love my mom and dad.
This is my prayer, my wish...
Know that I'm by your side, Homura.
I have to go meet the others!

I will bear all of your
cursed destinies!

Magical Girls make
hopes and dreams come true!

Don't give up, everyone!
I'll show you the way!
What a relief! Everyone's okay, right?
I won't give up hope.
You don't need to despair.
It's all right. Everything's going to be okay.

chara.description: A Magical Girl from Mitakihara who always has her finger on the pulse of everything in order to hype up Magia Record. At first she was on a mission to make Iroha into a worthy protagonist, but nowadays the two of them simply freewheel around Kamihama in a reckless blur.

charaMessageList.message: This asphalt's scorching hot!
Magia Stones... Also good for apologies!
This is my take on Magia Record.

FREE kitchen supplies for girls
who are picked!
Iroha's gotten sooo buff.
This just in on Magia Record!
Where's that awful little Incubator?
Ma! Gi! Repo! Did you all join in?
Ma! Gi! Reco! Did you all join in?
This is the true power of a senpai.
I'll bring this home as a souvenir.

chara.title: Swimsuit
chara.description: A Magical Girl who is just enjoying her summer vacation with her friends. This may seem like a normal swimsuit, but it's actually her Magical Girl outfit - and the fishing rod is her weapon. She's no pro fisher, but she'll reel in even the hugest of fish if it's for her friends' sakes.

charaMessageList.message: Eek! Th-the waves splashed me...
What sea creature is your favorite?

Oww... The beach ball hit me
right in the face...

What comes to mind when you
think of the sea? I wonder...
I got all kinds of bait ready to fish with.
The sea is kind of scary at night...

The sound of the waves is so lovely.
I could listen to it forever...
I thought the fish might just take the bait and go.
I won't let the heat bring me down!
Now I can fish in peace!
I caught a huge one! And I didn't get hurt!

doppel.description: The master of this emotion wound up on the beach during her trips of trial and error through time. She's got a holiday vibe, maybe due to the summer sun. By absorbing strange skills from the alien she has trapped on her straw hat, she conjures a palm tree that fires rounds of coconuts. No Witch would enjoy being pelted with supersonic coconuts, and the Doppel's attacks are guaranteed to hit due to the game mechanics, so they forfeit the moment it aims. The palm tree boasts high accuracy and it can target and hit a lone enemy repeatedly. Consider it an improvement.

chara.name: Holy Mami
chara.description: A Magical Girl from Mitakihara, and a mentor to Madoka and her friends. Though she was once proud of hunting Witches and saving people, she has relocated to Kamihama, where she works to lead Magical Girls to their liberation.

charaMessageList.message: I learned the truth...
I will not waver from this new path.
The justice I have put my faith in is here.

The tea I drink before battle is
a symbol of my determination.
My Florence is just darling, no?
I always wanted to use a tea set like this.
More people, more sweets to prepare...
I hope you are a little happier now.
This is the path I have laid out for you.
I will not allow anyone else to despair.
My wish is sacred.@I will allow no one to disparage it.

doppel.description: The master of this emotion has accepted salvation in a moment of despair on the darkest of nights. As a result, she was miraculously given the strength to overcome the fear and anxiety that she once had. Due to the mental state of it's master, this pitiful Doppel's appearance has changed, leading it to believe it can be a savior. Tiro Saint Doppelion is a symbol that represents a new hope for all girls in despair.

chara.title: Swimsuit
chara.description: A Magical Girl enjoying the summer sun and sea. Although she usually can't swim, this Magical Girl Form allows her to do so, so well she can even catch fish while doing it. Powerful as ever, she uses her beachball to rain fire upon her enemies, especially Mitama.

charaMessageList.message: Weather's greatâ€¦ Perfect for swimming.
Summer vacation? I'm always on vacation.
We can dive into the water over there!
Ramune tastes better after a nice swim.
Humans aren't made to float.
Is that a wind chime? It's so soothing...

You want me to keep an eye on
you while you swim?
That wasn't even a warm-up.
My spikes are pretty good, aren't they?
I'm not one to be beaten by the summer heat, so...
*Phew* I could use some nice, cold ramune right now!

doppel.description: The master of this emotion does not trust its mysterious power, but she cannot hide her excitement over finally being able to swim. Although its master typically despises Doppels, this Doppel uses hypnotic magic to give her the illusion that she can swim. Her excitement is apparent in its attack as well. When sunlight hits the mirror on its back, it concentrates all that energy into a beam that it rains down on its enemies. As soon as it has dealt with them, its master rides the candlestick holder sea turtle, and swims freely with the fish of the sea.

chara.name: Kanoko Yayoi
chara.description: A Magical Girl who wants to become a fashion designer. The only child of a family that runs a sheet metal plant, her parents' expectations that she will take over the business stress her out. Although she gets strange looks, she is always serious.

chara.description: A Magical Girl who wants to look adorable in any situation. She works as a maid at a maid cafe, shooting beams of cuteness with all her might. However, she has unintentionally become a comical personality, due to her old-fashioned style of acting.

charaMessageList.message:
It's Ikumi, your most favoritest
Kamihama maid!

I'm gonna melt aaall your hearts
with my charm!

Let's play a game! Ready?
Look oveeer...there!

Hey!
Who just called me old-fashioned?!
My dream is made from two wishes...

I can't deny what happened
right in front of me...

I would resort to anything,
even if it's someone else's way out...
Waaaaaah! That was super scary!
I've gotta get back to the cafe, my show's about to start!
I won't die... Not until your dream comes true...
My warmth and extra-special love will never fade away!

chara.description: A blue-blooded Magical Girl whose father is an ex-parliament member. Oriko does whatever it takes to get the job done, but her strong sense of justice, inherited from her father, keeps her from overdoing it. She is refined and loves drinking tea at home.

charaMessageList.message:
Do I see some disturbances
in my path ahead?

This is a future I've never seen before...
what is this?

No matter what path we take,
we end up in the same place.
I know exactly what I have to do!
You shall serve and protect me forever!

Everyone only sees me as Hisaomi Mikuni's
daughter, and nothing elseâ€¦

There is only one thing to do...
Eliminate Madoka Kaname.
Checkmate.
Still have your will to resist?
Repent!
Would you like to be my pawn too?

doppel.description: The master of this emotion has been given the duty of changing the fortold future. A strong wind blows, scattering flowers, the petals of which drift into another world. When the mist at last accumulates, the time comes. It intermingles with the fluttering flower petals, and the festivities begin. The Doppel starts to dance, and at the dance's climax, the enemy shadows vanish like flowers in a storm as an offering to the festivities.

chara.name: Kirika Kure
chara.description: Oriko's loyal servant, Kirika is a dangerous Magical Girl who doesn't hesitate when acting for her queen, no matter how immoral the deed. She is known as the "Dark Magical Girl" but her mind is pure like a child's. She even has a sweet tooth like one.

charaMessageList.message: Oriko...so merciful, you always forgive me...
I became a Magical Girl to be with you.
I will use this power for you, and you alone.
Enough! Die and atone for your sins!
Oriko, quickly, give me orders!
Just ask, I'll be anything for you!
Ah...so this is what true love is like!
What? You're done already?
As to be expected.
Hey, that was actually kind of fun.
Don't underestimate my love.

This act represents its extreme devotion, such that it offers up everything, including its life to its benefactor, while symbolizing the perilousness of its dependence upon the other, which it cannot maintain its identity without. The sharper the needles are, the more the stitches there are, and the harder it becomes to extricate oneself from it. However, this merely serves as an expression of the master's desire.

chara.name: Yuma Chitose
chara.description: A young Magical Girl who is very attached to Kyoko, Yuma sees her as her sister, and is willing to do anything for her. Although she is an innocent child, she was abused badly, and experiences terror much more distinctly than others, due to that trauma.

charaMessageList.message:
Just like Kyubey said,
I became a Magical Girl!
Pleaseâ€¦ Don't leave meâ€¦
I can use healing magic!
If Kyoko gets hurt, I'll make her better!

I want to become a Magical Girl
and fight, too!
I became a Magical Girl for Kyoko.
I can be useful too!
I won? Yay!
Tell me how good a girl I am!
I can fight too!
See? I'm helpful!

chara.description: A Magical Girl from Asunaro City who lost her memory. She lives with her teammates, Umika Misaki and Kaoru Maki. Food is a huge motivation for her. Not only does she like to eat, she's a skilled cook too. Her hair points to where Witches are.

charaMessageList.message: Cool, right? I can use magic!
Not all Witches used to be bad people.
Augh! I'm staaarving!
Umika! Kaoru! Dinner's ready!
W-we're gonna go to Kamihama City?

My name's Kazumi.
I still don't remember my last name.
Oh! Here! I sense a Witch!
Gosh... I'm really hungry...
Okay! Now let's go get something to eat!
We were totally breathing in sync!
I...can fight!

doppel.description: The master of this Doppel is much more particular about food than most. It wants to feed on anything within reach, and it does not care whether it eats Magical Girls or Witches. It is a chef born of the desire to eat itself, a Doppel of gluttony that devours all and returns it to nothingness. It has several plates prepared on its table at all times. Should you find yourself at its table on the battlefield, be careful you are not part of the mealâ€¦

chara.name: Umika Misaki
chara.description: A Magical Girl from Asunaro City who also works as a popular author, despite still being a student. She lives in a house with Kazumi and Kaoru Maki. The way she cures her writer's block is by cooking and shopping. She keeps all her manuscripts on her computer.

charaMessageList.message:
Are you ready?
Let's shop to our heart's content!
Are they really here...in Kamihama City?
Kazumi! Kaoru! Where are you two?!
Are you...a Kamihama Magical Girl?

The tougher the hurdle,
the calmer a novelist must be.
I set up my next plot twist...just so!
I've no patience for stories like that!
This wasn't such a bad outcome.
I'll put my pen down for a moment.
That ended just as I planned.
A natural conclusion.

chara.name: Kaoru Maki
chara.description: A Magical Girl from Asunaro City. She's a soccer player who is so good that people often say she will be the best player on the national team. She is great at using her athleticism to her advantage in battle. She wears a long-sleeved uniform even in summer.

charaMessageList.message: Heck yeaaah! Nice shot!
I wear long sleeves in summer, too!
Kazumi...Umika? Where'd they go?
Oh, me? I'm a soccer player.
Can't win unless you make your shots!
I won't miss... This is the best shot ever!
I can't stop...not at a time like this!
The game's over, fair and square!
This is a big win for us!
What an intense battle!
We won...but there's a lot more work to do.

chara.name: Darc
chara.description: A Magical Girl from medieval France known today as Jeanne d'Arc. Upon the death of her dear sister, Catherine, she resolved to save France from the brink of ruin. Simple, innocent, and trusting of others, she fondly refers to Qube (Kyubey) as "Monsieur Angel".

charaMessageList.message:
Miracles exist.
They have happened for me before.
I've wanted to meet you for a long time.
I'll continue to do what I can.
This is what I have the most faith in now!

That, too, was all because
I was not strong enough.
It's just as Monsieur Angel told me.
It was no problem at all. I'm glad you're safe.
Phew... We won.
Is everyone all right?!
Let's continue onward.
This is thanks to all of you.

doppel.description: The master of this Doppel has a pious heart, free of sin. The crosses that rain down from above are no ordinary ones. They are upside down crosses, and rather than exude divinity, they draw out sin and make those who bear witness to them face their own evil, wreathing them in purifying flame and burning them swiftly to ash. There is no sin that this Doppel cannot find and bring to light. Simply put, enemies have no choice but to accept its overwhelming purity.

chara.name: Liz
chara.description: A cool-headed Magical Girl from medieval Italy who uses shadow magic. In the midst of the Hundred Years' War, she fights alongside Darc and the French army to save France. Though she would never speak of it, she is said to be descended from a famous soldier.

charaMessageList.message: This is no dream.
Qube...you were an angel?
But really... That banner's design is just awful.
Darc really is a selfless girl.
I'm a mercenary. I came here from Italy.

La Pucelle, they call her.
Darc's become quite popular.
You're sure she is the one?
That was close, but we won.
I guess that will do.
You must stay focused.

I won't allow you to
extinguish the light!

doppel.title: Feature: Shadow
doppel.description: The master of this Doppel feels deep sympathy for others, even at the most dire of times. Where there is light, there is dark. This is providence. But it is also providence that those who are blanketed in shadow will never have light shined upon them. This is a Doppel that stands beside the hero as their shadow, surrounded by their dazzling brilliance. It is the elusive shadow itself, and yet, it is exactly what makes the light shine so brightly. The two are connected by an unbreakable bond.

chara.name: Melissa
chara.description: A Magical Girl of medieval France who serves in the war and attends to all of Darc's needs. She is the daughter of Captain "La Hire", who is a comrade-in-arms of Jeanne d'Arc. Though normally a kind and well-mannered girl, her fury cannot be stopped when she becomes angered.

charaMessageList.message: I will stay by Darc's side.
Both Darc and Liz are my dear friends.

That is "La Pucelle".
She is nothing less than a miracle.
You mustn't drink too much, Father!
Stop! How could you kick Monsieur Angel?

One day I wish to see the village
where Darc was born.
I am not afraid to step on the battlefield.
We did it!
W-we won!
I'm happy we did...
I can't believe it!

doppel.title: Feature: Thundering Wrath
doppel.description: The master of this emotion is seen by all as mild-mannered and kind. Every action or force exerted upon another object results in a "reaction", and since this Doppel is a reaction to its master's personality, it appears as rage incarnate. It will disintegrate anything that stands in its path; the more her heart yearns for peace, the more violently its rage will gush forth. It would be wise not to underestimate it just because it allows you to strike it without fighting back.

chara.name: Corbeau
chara.description: A masked Magical Girl who fights in the shadows for the English in the Hundred Years' War. The second sister of three, and like her mother, adores her family. This love does not spill over to her enemies, though. For nothing excites her more than a strong opponent, it's what she lives for.

charaMessageList.message: Come out, come out, wherever you areâ™ª
Now THIS is music to my ears!

Oh, I've been WAITING for you,
girl in black!
The hell?! Why's this light so powerful?!

Time to have my fun with
that ebon-clad girl!
Heh...heh heh! Not bad!

You're the first to have muddied
my Soul Gem!
Any complaints?
Done already? You're barely worth playing with.
Now you, you're fun. I had a GREAT time!
Well, that was a letdown.

Even as a daughter of the Roman emperor, she is able to forge deep friendships with the people she sees worthy. Just like snakes, she hates Qube (Kyubey).

charaMessageList.message: It's a pleasure, La Pucelle.

I can't believe I did
something so disgraceful!
Please, Darc, just call me Elisa.
She is trusting to a fault, that girl.
And...I'm not a princess anyway...
I envy you, to be honest.
Why is this happening?!
No need to thank me.
It appears this match has been decided.
Das Ende! It's all over.
There, that should take care of that.

Her sense of duty to carry out her knightly orders, as well as the accompanying pressure of those duties are encompassed within as well. When this dragon appears, it demonstrates her unrivaled might through a tyrannical rampage of trampled battlegrounds and rampant devouring.

chara.description: A Magical Girl who recently transferred to Akanegazaki. She has no parents and works part time to make a living. Although amiable and pleasant at school, she bears the cold face of an assassin once classes are over. Her target: Magical Girls. A tragic past lies concealed in her closed off heart.

charaMessageList.message: It's up to you if you believe me or not.
I know what they call me. "Assassin".
Why are you being so nice to me?

You learned the truth about
Magical Girls, didn't you?
Delivery complete.

Have you ever hated someone
enough to kill them?
I refuse to turn into a Witch!
Farewell.
I'm doing the right thing.
After all these attempts...the result's the same.
You can't win against me.

doppel.title: Feature: Mayfly
doppel.description: A flame blazes within the master of this Doppel. It rages with her desire for vengeance, affirming her bond with the woman who once took care of her. While its fiery pillar is meant to exterminate the Witches she loathes so much, it also scorches its host, who bears the burden of a callous fate. Perhaps the fact that it takes the form of a mayfly represents the brevity of its host's life? That may be why its bells reverberate through to the very souls of those who hear them. What does she see beyond the flickering flames? Only she who controls them can say.

chara.name: Arisa Narumi
chara.description: One in a team of 4 Magical Girls who attend school at Akanegazaki. Rambunctious, she hates to study, and her rough, sloppy manner is always criticized by her friend Chisato. She was a completely different person, extremely timid and shy, before becoming a Magical Girl.

charaMessageList.message: You looking for a fight?!
Whoa... Magical Girl powers are awesome!
Ooh... 'Kay, we'll catch the perpetrator!
Yeah, so I'm always alone. Big deal...
Eh, it's just a greeting, not a speech!
Cool, let's start patrolling!
I'm going to the arcade after school!
Uuugh... Sooo bored.
I gotta rush home and take a shower.
These punks are too weak to be starting fights!
Face it, I'm getting way too strong!

chara.name: Chisato Shion
chara.description: One in a team of 4 Magical Girls who attend school at Akanegazaki. Levelheaded and calm, she values being ethical above all else. While she may come off as cold, she has a caring side for her friends, having reformed Arisa's former bad behavior. Her father used to write and draw picture books.

charaMessageList.message:
Unexcused absences AND fighting?
I can't ignore this!
My dad was a picture book author.
I wish I was like Haruka, kind and bright.
Arisa, you were late AGAIN!
These weird rumors are disturbing.
Thanks, you know just what to say.
My name? Why should I tell you?
Whew... All finished.
I'm glad you got my point.
This is because we worked as a team!
*Sigh* That was fast!

charaMessageList.message: Nanoha Takamachi, ready for battle!
Let's keep moving...straight forward!

I want to be stronger...
stronger than I am now.
This is for anyone who's out there crying ...
There's something I want to protect.
You're never really alone.
I'm doing great and smiling everyday!
I, Nanoha Takamachi, will never give in!
Good job! I knew you would win!
We won! Now it's time to talk.
I can't lose! I have things I need to protect...

charaMessageList.message: Straight ahead, don't hesitate!
I'm not alone, I can keep going!

My memories, and my future...
All of it's so important to me.
No sweat! I'm not doing this alone!
I'm fine. I'm strong, y'see?

Gather all your courage,
and take one step forward!
I'll get stronger, even stronger than before!
Successfully neutralized the target. Phew...
Good work. Let's keep it up.
We won! Is everyone all right?
Thank you, everyone. This is all thanks to you.
